<li><b>Optimization over zonotopes and training support vector machines</b>.<br>
<a href="//www.parc.xerox.com/csl/members/bern/">M. Bern</a>
and D. Eppstein.<br>
<a href="//arxiv.org/abs/cs.CG/0105017">arXiv:cs.CG/0105017</a>.<br>
<a href="BerEpp-WADS-01-svm.ps.gz"><i>7th Worksh. Algorithms and Data
